docs/STATUS.md is a task backlog for a stenography system (likely Plover-related, given "tabstops" and "strokes"), tracked as impact and difficulty. It documents five open issues: a vim snippet bug with duplicate anchor points, missing Array<> type-skipping in %t contexts, stroke notation for tuple types, unification of C++ dictionary handling with static dicts via a new %T marker, and a menuing system for dict selection.